text:
(1) East River, at Battery Park, showing Pier 1, the Staten Island Ferry landing and its fog bell. Also shown (background, right to left) are; the 60 Wall Street Tower, City Bank Farmers Trust Co. and Bank of Manhattan Trust Co. Buildings. June 27, 1934.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) Part of the same, at an earlier date. The building under construction is the City Bank Farmers Trust Co. Building. September 1930.

P. L. Sperr.

(3) The same. January 1938.

P. L. Sperr.
title: East River - Pier 1 - Battery Park, Manhattan - [Bank of Manhattan - City Bank-Farmers Trust Company - 60 Wall Street Tower.]
